{"tid":997573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15年修成正果，現實中各對青梅竹馬愛情果然好嚮往","createTime":"2019-01-27T09:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T09:51:39.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"131989246ea9112a22e2e78019b421582e0d548c","tid":997573,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"所謂「青梅竹馬」專指因為住得近的一男一女、從小一起長大玩在一起的關係，當然這種近水樓台先得越的距離，絕對免不了會摩擦產生出戀愛情愫啊～<br />\n<br />\n像是喪女最愛看的日本動漫宅作品，經常會出現以青梅竹馬為題材的男女主角！<br />\n<br />\n而且青梅竹馬的好處超多啊，像是知道彼此的喜好和夢想..<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201762.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201762.jpg&h=210b9293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爬陽台過去叫人家起床（傳Line？！當然是Body鬧鐘更勝一籌啊！）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201765.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201765.jpg&h=2bce9b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真是拿妳沒辦法啊～誰叫我從小就在照顧妳了呢～的責任感！<br />\n<br />\n超羨慕啊！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐美其實也有啊，像是住在那種比較有錢的、一戶獨棟的小鎮，也會經常和鄰居成為青梅竹馬，而且國外民情還更開放，所以讓他們自由發展感情到最後，只要沒出亂子，１５年後直接步入禮堂也是有可能的～～根本就是彼此父母內定好的女婿跟媳婦嘛！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201768.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201768.jpg&h=b0cb8e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201767.jpg&h=69eb9cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201764.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201764.jpg&h=e7649b14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201758.jpg&h=8946b29e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201759.jpg&h=45ecb200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n註:美斯老婆是破鞋,mk仔玩完後,毒撚美斯埋單<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201760.jpg&h=632e95ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這對比較弱，才ㄍ一ㄥ了七年，可是男生的反轉讓喪女覺得非常有意思＞////＜<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201766.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201766.jpg&h=a5419c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1201/d1201763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1201%2Fd1201763.jpg&h=eda1920d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青梅竹馬因為彼此最熟悉了解，不免會經過情人＞家人＞情人的心裡矛盾期，但是只要跨過那檻，就是彼此最熟悉的愛人和家人，超棒的！"},{"pid":"e8a11fd1fad421dd1dc6226575819160dd7eeb12","tid":997573,"uid":185651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:44:27.000Z","msg":"毒撚同自己隻左手都係青梅竹馬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2f5e58f85e77186c66b550809705ab52a8935f","tid":997573,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:51:39.000Z","msg":"樣靚就ok<br />\n<br />\n你試下－對樣衰"}]}